channel.title: What About the Starters?
channel.description:
Ive been looking over the RS2 Server Tutorial board and I see all these tutorials for people who have a good experience in coding. But what about the people who want to make a server and need some basic tutorials for them to use. What are they suppose to do? Plus I need some basic tutorials my self =[.
I wonder..
- Boring
